{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the initial state of a pack. The state of a pack becomes known by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the time the shared "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object sends the first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackProgressChangedNotification","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" about the pack. For inactive"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"packs, you must explicitly request a progress update using the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack\/requestProgress","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An invalid pack always has a state of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateInvalid","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":", never"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackState\/MLNOfflinePackStateUnknown","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"It is unknown whether the pack is inactive, active, or complete."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackstate\/mlnofflinepackstateunknown"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},